<P>
   BBO-TRADES _ The last day that a major leaguer can be traded and
still be eligible for the postseason and several trades could be
made on Sat. and Sun. Watching to see if Braves make another move
(middle infielder?). (Stinson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
