   POLITICAL NEWS (``p'' category)
</P>
<P>
   CVN-CONVENTION-CHENEY (Philadelphia) _ Vice presidential hopeful
Dick Cheney arrives for the Republican national convention and
addresses a GOP pep rally at a downtown hotel. Earlier on the
Sunday TV talk shows, Cheney defended his controversial votes in
Congress on freeing Nelson Mandela and easy-to-smuggle plastic
guns. However, he said he might vote differently if the same issues
came up now. By DAN FREEDMAN.
