<HEADLINE>
DIVIDEND MEETINGS 
</HEADLINE>
   c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Following is a partial list of dividend meetings for this week:
</P>
<P>
   MONDAY
</P>
<P>
   American Sts Wtr Co
</P>
<P>
   Highwoods Pptys Inc
</P>
<P>
