morning talk shows; then shows up for a rally in Philadelphia. 800
words. By Eric Schmitt.
</P>
<P>
   GOP-DC-DELEGATE (Washington) _ A look at the loneliest
Republican convention delegate: the one from Washington, D.C.,
where 19 out of 20 voters are Democrats. By Philip Shenon.
</P>
