Convention, arrives here and discusses his views of the GOP ticket
and platform in an interview. Earlier, U.S. Rep. Dave Camp, U.S.
Sen. Spencer Abraham and Michigan Gov. John Engler said the party
will carry the state handily. By Eric Rosenberg.
