<HEADLINE>
E-COMMERCE: DOT-COM EMPLOYEES GROWING IN NUMBER AND BECOMING MORE
SELECTIVE 
</HEADLINE>
  (ART ADV: Photo NYT 7 is being sent to NYT graphics clients.
Nonsubscribers can purchase one-time rights by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.) 
 By BOB TEDESCHI   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   If executives of e-commerce companies thought they were having a
