<P>
   BC-OBIT-TUKEY-NYT (moved Thursday, July 27)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service obituary sent on Thursday, July 27
about John Wilder Tukey, a statistician, referred incompletely to a
book being edited by Fred R. Shapiro that will credit Tukey with
having coined the word ``software.'' It will be a dictionary of
quotations with information on the origin of terms, not solely
about the origin of terms.
